description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/arc-raiders/

The surface is calling; your adventure starts now.
As a Raider, prepare to leave the safety of Speranza’s settlements to scavenge the ruins above. ARC machines are a threat, but every run to the surface offers a chance to build something new. Battle for high stakes loot and risk it all in this expansion Extraction Adventure from Embark Studios. Your journey is just beginning.

ARC Raiders launches October 30th! Watch the launch trailer and prepare to head topside.
